data.title: Nasdaq rose by 1% on strong Amazon and Apple earnings, Dow Jones flat on Friday. Palantir and Robinhood also saw gains.
data.description: Today, the stock market remained steady with the Dow Jones index staying flat. This was influenced by the notable performance of tech giants Amazon and Apple, whose stocks surged following robust earnings reports. Meanwhile, the Nasdaq saw a significant increase of 1%, driven by the impressive earnings of Amazon and Apple. Additionally, companies like Palantir and Robinhood experienced notable jumps in their stock prices. Overall, these developments were closely followed by investors and market watchers.

data.title: Roku stock soars on big earnings beat, surpassing Q3 expectations and guidance, boosting investor confidence.
data.description: Roku's stock experienced a significant increase on Friday following the release of their third-quarter results, which surpassed expectations. The streaming video platform saw a surge in its stock value, fueled by better-than-expected earnings and guidance. This positive performance resonated well with investors, resulting in an uptick in Roku's stock price. The company's strong showing in the third quarter contributed to this spike, showcasing growth and potential in the streaming video industry. Investors responded positively to this news, leading to a notable jump in Roku's stock.
